\section{Introduction}
Clinical consultations between doctors and patients typically has a rich mix of essential details - including symptoms, diagnostic reasoning, medication histories, treatment decisions, and relevant psychosocial context - all of which are vital for accurate documentation and continuity of care. Automating the summarization of these clinical interactions can significantly ease documentation workloads, enhance provider efficiency, and support more seamless continuity of care across the patient’s treatment journey. 
